## ğŸ“ˆ Dashboards & Insights

### ğŸ—“ 1. Monthly Sales Trend (Â£)
![Monthly Sales Trend](images/monthly_sales_trend.png)

**Build Summary**
- `Invoice Date` â†’ Columns (by Month)  
- `SUM(Sales)` â†’ Rows  
- Add labels (formatted as Â£, no decimals)

**Insights**
- Sales increase sharply from **September to December**, peaking in **November (Â£1.17M)**.  
- Strong **Q4 seasonality** suggests higher demand during holidays and year-end promotions.

