### ğŸ› 3. Top 10 Products by Sales (Â£)
![Top 10 Products](images/top_products.png)

**Build Summary**
- `Description` â†’ Rows  
- `SUM(Sales)` â†’ Columns  
- Filter: **Top 10** by sales  
- Add data labels (formatted Â£, no decimals)

**Insights**
- **â€œWhite Hanging Heart T-Light Holderâ€** and **â€œRegency Cake Stand 3 Tierâ€** are best sellers.  
- Product sales are highly concentrated â€” top products drive most of the revenue.  
